00:17:13.640 --> 00:17:14.920
What's wrong with my hair?

00:17:17.039 --> 00:17:17.680
Alright

00:17:26.519 --> 00:17:27.200
What's up?

00:17:27.400 --> 00:17:27.920
Sis.

00:17:28.119 --> 00:17:29.000
My brother-in-law told me

00:17:29.000 --> 00:17:30.279
to tidy up the house a bit.

00:17:30.359 --> 00:17:31.240
He said he wants to surprise you.

00:17:31.759 --> 00:17:32.599
Come home a bit later.

00:17:33.960 --> 00:17:34.599
Go ahead, do your thing.

00:17:34.640 --> 00:17:35.200
As for me,

00:17:35.559 --> 00:17:36.640
I can't get back right now.

00:17:37.160 --> 00:17:37.799
I'm busy.

00:17:38.079 --> 00:17:38.680
That's great.

00:17:42.480 --> 00:17:43.200
Charles.

00:17:44.240 --> 00:17:45.039
Your dad

00:17:45.279 --> 00:17:46.240
wants you to come home.

00:17:46.240 --> 00:17:47.400
Don't be too anxious.

00:17:47.440 --> 00:17:48.319
He's just lonely.

00:17:48.559 --> 00:17:49.200
Yeah.

00:17:49.200 --> 00:17:50.720
He's really lonely.

00:17:51.559 --> 00:17:52.720
The urgent thing

00:17:52.720 --> 00:17:54.880
is you should find him a companion.

00:17:54.920 --> 00:17:55.960
He'd be so happy.

00:17:56.680 --> 00:17:58.200
He'd be happy,

00:17:58.319 --> 00:18:00.160
