00:18:01.559 --> 00:18:02.640
Mom's still here.

00:18:02.640 --> 00:18:03.279
So...

00:18:04.359 --> 00:18:04.960
Then

00:18:05.279 --> 00:18:06.279
get him a dog.

00:18:06.599 --> 00:18:08.000
Right? They're so cute.

00:18:08.400 --> 00:18:11.200
It could even attract customers to your restaurant.

00:18:11.519 --> 00:18:13.039
What's your restaurant called?

00:18:13.759 --> 00:18:15.119
Piaoxiang Dog Meat Restaurant.

00:18:17.960 --> 00:18:19.319
Then buy two houses.

00:18:19.839 --> 00:18:21.240
One in Sanya,

00:18:21.319 --> 00:18:22.880
one in Qiqihar.

00:18:23.160 --> 00:18:24.599
Go to Sanya in summer,

00:18:24.880 --> 00:18:26.359
Qiqihar in winter.

00:18:26.519 --> 00:18:27.720
That'll guarantee a long life.

00:18:28.839 --> 00:18:30.160
Mom, you're something else.

00:18:30.319 --> 00:18:32.759
How do you manage to step on a landmine
with every sentence?

00:18:33.519 --> 00:18:34.279
Sis.

00:18:34.400 --> 00:18:35.839
That's not fair of you to say.

00:18:36.119 --> 00:18:37.279
Even though my Aunt Cai

00:18:37.359 --> 00:18:38.839
comes up with terrible ideas,

00:18:39.000 --> 00:18:40.680
her intentions are good.

00:18:40.880 --> 00:18:42.279
You're being a bit harsh.

00:18:42.759 --> 00:18:43.920
I'm harsh?

00:18:44.519 --> 00:18:45.599
Look at Aunt Cai—

00:18:45.759 --> 00:18:48.160
she's been saying it's your birthday
since early morning.

00:18:48.200 --> 00:18:50.640
She went out early to buy fish and groceries.

00:18:50.640 --> 00:18:52.279
She even paid for your hair styling.

00:18:52.400 --> 00:18:53.519
Spent half the day fussing.

00:18:53.519 --> 00:18:55.599
But you went off with your husband.

00:18:55.720 --> 00:18:57.319
Is that fair to her?

00:18:57.480 --> 00:18:58.480
It's not me, it's just—

00:18:59.359 --> 00:19:00.640
As long as my daughter is happy,

00:19:00.960 --> 00:19:02.119
I'm fine with anything.

00:19:03.279 --> 00:19:04.079
Aunt Cai.

00:19:04.480 --> 00:19:05.960
Parents as thoughtful as you

00:19:05.960 --> 00:19:06.799
are rare these days.

00:19:07.279 --> 00:19:08.200
How about this—

00:19:08.480 --> 00:19:09.880
I'll make you my godmother.

00:19:10.640 --> 00:19:12.200
That's wonderful!

00:19:12.720 --> 00:19:14.680
Today is truly a great day.

00:19:15.440 --> 00:19:16.200
Not only did I

00:19:16.279 --> 00:19:17.319
give birth to Li Li,

00:19:17.519 --> 00:19:19.519
I also gained a godson.

00:19:19.920 --> 00:19:22.079
You two should celebrate together.

00:19:22.519 --> 00:19:23.240
Li Li.

00:19:23.400 --> 00:19:24.480
Call him brother.

00:19:24.720 --> 00:19:25.480
Say "brother."

00:19:29.240 --> 00:19:30.599
Just shave my head.

00:19:30.599 --> 00:19:31.759
You two celebrate, I'll become a monk.

00:19:38.079 --> 00:19:38.680
Li Li.

00:19:39.039 --> 00:19:39.640
Li Li.

00:19:39.960 --> 00:19:41.359
Don't be mad.

00:19:42.000 --> 00:19:43.920
I was just chatting with the neighbor.

00:19:43.960 --> 00:19:45.200
I never said

00:19:45.240 --> 00:19:47.799
I'd make Charles my godson.

00:19:47.839 --> 00:19:49.160
I'm confused too.

00:19:49.559 --> 00:19:51.119
Back then,

00:19:51.119 --> 00:19:52.799
when you were cold and mean,

00:19:53.440 --> 00:19:54.920
our mother-daughter bond was bad.

00:19:55.160 --> 00:19:56.559
Now you're warm-hearted,

00:19:57.160 --> 00:19:59.400
but our relationship still isn't good.

00:20:00.880 --> 00:20:03.079
I must've been awful before.

00:20:03.559 --> 00:20:05.079
Did you forget? Back then,

00:20:05.480 --> 00:20:06.200
all through my childhood,

00:20:06.519 --> 00:20:07.680
you never cared for me.

00:20:08.079 --> 00:20:09.799
Only criticism, never praise.

00:20:10.160 --> 00:20:11.519
Sarcasm counted as affection.

00:20:11.519 --> 00:20:12.960
Putting me down meant you cared.

00:20:15.559 --> 00:20:17.839
Seems I'm really not a good person.

00:20:18.359 --> 00:20:20.039
It's not all your fault.

00:20:20.440 --> 00:20:21.680
Our home planet is just like that.

00:20:22.519 --> 00:20:23.480
You and Dad—

00:20:24.039 --> 00:20:25.640
weren't happy together,

00:20:25.880 --> 00:20:27.319
but not sad apart either.

00:20:28.319 --> 00:20:29.480
I don't want that for myself.

00:20:31.200 --> 00:20:33.359
Sounds like our family has big issues.

00:20:33.720 --> 00:20:35.359
And no one to mediate.

00:20:36.119 --> 00:20:36.960
So,

00:20:37.319 --> 00:20:38.640
no matter how advanced a planet is,

00:20:38.839 --> 00:20:40.240
it needs a neighborhood committee.

00:20:40.920 --> 00:20:42.240
Our planet doesn't have one.

00:20:42.279 --> 00:20:44.640
That's why our planet is way behind Earth.

00:20:44.640 --> 00:20:46.039
You really like Earth, huh?

00:20:47.200 --> 00:20:49.599
But you'll have to return to the home planet for work.

00:20:49.799 --> 00:20:51.119
What about Meng Hang?

00:20:53.200 --> 00:20:54.319
I've been thinking—

00:20:54.400 --> 00:20:56.599
I'll apply to stay with the editorial department.

00:20:57.400 --> 00:20:59.640
If that doesn't work, I'll quit.

00:21:00.119 --> 00:21:01.680
I have a job on Earth anyway.

00:21:03.480 --> 00:21:04.400
You've really decided?

00:21:04.920 --> 00:21:06.160
Not going back to the home planet?

00:21:11.720 --> 00:21:12.599
I've made up my mind.

00:21:13.640 --> 00:21:15.119
I truly love Meng Hang.

00:21:15.759 --> 00:21:17.000
So I can't leave him.

00:21:18.599 --> 00:21:19.880
Plus, there's his dad,

00:21:19.920 --> 00:21:21.279
and all my friends.

00:21:21.640 --> 00:21:22.920
I can't bear to leave.

00:21:24.519 --> 00:21:26.119
I don't know what's wrong with me.

00:21:26.519 --> 00:21:28.359
Why am I so fragile now?

00:21:29.519 --> 00:21:30.680
Maybe

00:21:30.799 --> 00:21:32.920
that's Earth's superpower.

00:21:33.599 --> 00:21:34.480
What?

00:21:34.920 --> 00:21:36.359
The thing you just mentioned—

00:21:36.920 --> 00:21:37.599
Love.

00:22:02.440 --> 00:22:03.920
Li Li, you look beautiful today.

00:22:06.440 --> 00:22:08.119
This hairstyle suits you perfectly.

00:22:08.200 --> 00:22:09.119
Really?

00:22:09.839 --> 00:22:11.759
I prepared these photos of us.

00:22:12.000 --> 00:22:12.599
Take a look.

00:22:24.319 --> 00:22:24.920
Come on, come on.

00:22:27.039 --> 00:22:29.039
See what I've got ready.

00:22:29.680 --> 00:22:30.279
Come.

00:22:31.960 --> 00:22:32.480
Sit.

00:22:36.119 --> 00:22:36.799
Thank you.

00:22:43.720 --> 00:22:44.519
Thank you.

00:22:45.559 --> 00:22:46.079
Sis.

00:22:46.359 --> 00:22:47.079
Happy birthday.

00:22:49.359 --> 00:22:50.079
Thank you.

00:22:51.559 --> 00:22:52.839
Why are you here?

00:22:52.960 --> 00:22:54.240
To join your birthday party.

00:22:56.960 --> 00:22:58.200
What party?

00:22:58.240 --> 00:22:59.799
Can't you see this is

00:22:59.960 --> 00:23:01.279
