Let me be fair here.

00:23:19.680 --> 00:23:20.200
Use my chopsticks.

00:23:20.200 --> 00:23:21.640
Have a shrimp first.

00:23:23.319 --> 00:23:24.920
Once you start, you won't stop. Hurry.

00:23:24.920 --> 00:23:25.319
I'll eat everything.

