What's this?

00:25:16.920 --> 00:25:17.920
Cake.

00:25:18.400 --> 00:25:19.400
There's writing on it.

00:25:20.000 --> 00:25:20.680
Wishing

00:25:21.200 --> 00:25:24.839
Li Li a happy birthday.

00:25:25.000 --> 00:25:25.720
Mom.

