Mom, sit down and eat with us.

00:25:56.720 --> 00:25:57.240
No, thanks.

00:25:57.319 --> 00:25:58.920
I'm going to the pet shop.

00:25:59.039 --> 00:26:00.359
No, the pet shop is closed.

00:26:01.079 --> 00:26:02.720
Those little animals haven't eaten yet.

00:26:09.079 --> 00:26:10.480
When we first met...

00:26:10.839 --> 00:26:11.480
That day...

00:26:11.480 --> 00:26:12.359
Wait a moment.

00:26:14.480 --> 00:26:15.079
Mom.

00:26:18.960 --> 00:26:19.599
Mom.

00:26:22.319 --> 00:26:23.160
Don't go yet.

00:26:23.279 --> 00:26:23.960
Wait for me.

00:26:32.559 --> 00:26:33.319
Meng Hang.

00:26:36.640 --> 00:26:37.720
Thank you for preparing

00:26:37.720 --> 00:26:38.960
such a wonderful birthday for me.

00:26:40.000 --> 00:26:41.279
I'm really touched.

00:26:41.960 --> 00:26:42.880
I promise you,

00:26:43.680 --> 00:26:45.759
from now on, we'll spend every birthday together.

00:26:46.279 --> 00:26:46.960
For a lifetime.

00:26:48.720 --> 00:26:50.839
I'll be just as thoughtful as you were today.

00:26:52.279 --> 00:26:53.759
But tonight,

00:26:55.960 --> 00:26:57.400
I want to spend it with my mom.

00:26:58.319 --> 00:26:59.039
Is that okay?

