As long as you're happy.

00:27:11.599 --> 00:27:12.519
Then I'll go keep Li Cai company.

00:27:14.160 --> 00:27:15.559
Keep him in, don't let him out.

00:27:18.079 --> 00:27:18.640
Don't worry.

00:27:28.119 --> 00:27:28.599
Mom.

00:27:29.200 --> 00:27:29.799
Come in.

00:27:30.079 --> 00:27:30.559
What is it?

00:27:30.839 --> 00:27:31.640
It's your birthday.

00:27:32.240 --> 00:27:32.960
No, no, no.

00:27:32.960 --> 00:27:34.200
You celebrate with Xiao Meng.

00:27:34.200 --> 00:27:35.319
No Xiao Meng.

00:27:36.319 --> 00:27:37.079
Just the two of us.

00:27:38.480 --> 00:27:42.079
Happy birthday to you.

00:27:42.720 --> 00:27:46.160
Happy birthday to you.

00:27:46.799 --> 00:27:50.759
Happy birthday to you.

00:27:51.160 --> 00:27:55.720
Happy birthday to you.

00:27:57.039 --> 00:27:58.759
I hope my daughter

00:27:59.240 --> 00:28:01.799
is as happy every day as she is today.

00:28:03.200 --> 00:28:05.720
Then I wish my mom

00:28:06.119 --> 00:28:07.960
can be like today every day.

00:28:09.200 --> 00:28:10.000
This child...

